Popular Nollywood child star-turned-billionaire wife Regina Daniels has been hospitalised once again for the third time in a span of few weeks.  In May, The Nation had reported the actress was back to the hospital weeks after she underwent successful surgery in April for an undisclosed ailment. However, the actress revealed on her social media page on Tuesday that she’s back to the hospital and is quite sad about it. Sharing a photo of her bandaged wrist with plaster on and several medical items scattered around, the mother of one captioned post: “Man down again” accompanied with a sad emoji.  Source Popular Nollywood child star-turned-billionaire wife Regina Daniels has been hospitalised. The actress is back to the hospital weeks after she underwent successful surgery for an undisclosed ailment. The mother of one updated fans on the state of her health via her Snapchat story She showed off a fully bandaged wrist… In "Entertainment" Teenage actress and wife of a billionaire, Regina Daniels appears to be making frantic efforts to put herself in the news again.   Popular Nollywood actress, Regina Daniels looks different as she flaunts her new butterfly tattoo on his back and new customized chain written her husband name on it Ned… In "Entertainment" Senator-elect for Delta North Senatorial District, Prince Ned Nwoko married all of his six wives as virgins, Regina Daniels being the newest of his wives, Frontline News Online has been told. According to sources close to the former member of the House of Representatives, he places chastity high on his… In "Entertainment"